                            <cell role="num">129</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5</cell>
                            <cell role="num">124</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Bolivia</cell>
                            <cell role="num">95</cell>
                            <cell role="num">32</cell>
                            <cell role="num">63</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Paraguay</cell>
                            <cell role="num">38</cell>
                            <cell role="num">10</cell>
                            <cell role="num">28</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>You are requested to bring the above points forcefully to the attention of the
                    appropriate government officials. An important service can thus be rendered to
                    the UNRRA program. This subject has been fully discussed with the British and
                    Canadian Governments, whose missions, the Department understands, will receive
                    similar instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
